{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"weak"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate>"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delegate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The delegate is responsible for responding to significant changes during the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"snapshotting process, such as the style loading. Implement a delegate to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"customize the style that is depicted by the snapshot.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You set the delegate after initializing the snapshotter but before receiving"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the snapshot, typically before starting the snapshot. The snapshotter keeps a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"weak reference to its delegate, so you must keep a strong reference to it to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"ensure that your style customizations apply."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/delegate"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The snapshotter’s delegate."}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/delegate","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot